CI/CD with Jenkins

Today's Focus: Automation pipeline.
What I Learned:

Jenkins setup

Pipeline as code

Automated testing

Code:

groovy
// Jenkinsfile
pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm install'
                sh 'npm run build'
            }
        }
        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm test'
            }
        }
        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm run deploy'
            }
        }
    }
}
